      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "主线叫main，然后从main分出一个newbranch。在newbranch上做一个关键提交，备注写成\"Pick me\"，这个提交后续要被cherry-pick回main。",
