      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先搭建基础结构：main初始提交，分出newbranch，checkout过去做\"Pick me\"提交。然后切回main再做一次提交，让两边都有进展。",
      "elements_involved": [
