    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这样main和newbranch就分叉了。接下来newbranch再做一个提交，然后切回main执行cherry-pick，把那个\"Pick me\"拿过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
